description: Calulates the ratio (fold change) between a control and treatment condition.
name: foldchange_app

model.description: Calculates the ratio (fold change) between a control and treatment condition.

factors.name: Measurement
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the values to use in the computation.

Example:
* log transform of S100
* log transformed and ComBat Corrected S100
* VSN transformed S100
* VSN transformed and ComBat Corrected S100

factors.name: Variable
factors.description:
Select the peptide identifier.

Example:
* ID

factors.name: Supergroup
factors.description:
Select factor(s) that identify separate pairing within which the fold change should be calculated. 

Example:
* Barcode
* Cell line
* Replicate
* Supergroup

factors.name: Group
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the comparison groups.

Example:
* Test Condition
* Treatment off chip
